ws, soap operas, books, and encyclopedias. By fostering an awareness of life outside North Korea and enhancing cultural knowledge, the materials these citizens disseminate are affecting the social and political consciousness of a people, as well as their everyday lives.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 05. Mai 2020) 0aMass media and culturezKorea (North) 0aMass media and culturezKorea (North). 0aMass media and international relations. 0aMass media and propaganda. 0aMass mediazKorea (North) 0aMass mediazKorea (North). 0aPopular culturezKorea (North) 0aPopular culturezKorea (North). 0aPropaganda. 7aHISTORY / Modern / 21st Century.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYUP eBook-Package 2016z978311066771440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300224474423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780300224474.jpg  a978-3-11-066771-4  YUP eBook-Package 2016b2016  aEBA_FAO  aGBV-deGruyter-alles